Invocation Name: times table speed test
des: A simple quiz type app for kids to practice the speed and accuracy of their times table. It gives you five random times table question from 2 X 2 up to 15 X 15 and tells you the total time taken to answer all five of them correctly.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
